--------------------
1. Use /app/ directory (App Router) instead of /pages/.
2. Modularize by feature, not by file type.
   Example:
     /app
       /dashboard
         page.tsx
         layout.tsx
         loading.tsx
         DashboardClient.tsx
         DashboardServer.ts
3. Use `lib/` and `services/` folders:
   - lib/: Utility and pure functions.
   - services/: Business logic, API calls, DB access.

